## Business Rules Summary

| Rule | Condition | Action |
|------|-----------|--------|
| **Qualification** | PropertyType, Urgency, Language, CampaignSource, Location, PriceRange | Score lead 1-10 |
| **Agent Assignment** | Spanish + Miami → Maria; PriceRange > $2M → Luxury Team; No match → General Pool + Flag | Auto-assign or escalate |
| **Escalation** | Score >= 9 | Manager approval required |
| **Compliance** | Commercial + High Urgency | Send to Compliance Review Agent |
| **Referral Bonus** | CampaignSource = Referral | Increase score by 2 |
| **Contracts** | All contract actions | Use DocuSign |
| **Urgent Notifications** | High urgency | Twilio SMS |
| **Policy Reference** | Any procedural question | Notion knowledge base |

